# Notification module

- Triggered exclusively by domain events via MediatR + outbox
- Channels: FCM/APNs (push), Twilio/Africa's Talking (SMS), SendGrid/SES (email)
- Per-user preferences in PostgreSQL; hot preferences in Redis (TTL 5min)
- Retry: up to 3 at 5-minute intervals via Hangfire; log final failed status
- Critical (emergency, medication reminders): SMS fallback if push fails (P30)
- Every sent notification → `NotificationLog` (P29)
- Next-of-kin: max 3 retries; never exceed 3 (P23)
